name: Courage Peace Love Ukraine
description:
We stand in solidarity with Ukraine in courage, peace, and love.

I designed this glitch art video with licensed AI music to support the humanitarian efforts in Ukraine.


The piece is created for the #Glitch4Ukraine in association with Tezos Community Glitch Artist Showcase hosted by Eso Tero @TerosEso @rblbab @sonrefniocsid

100% of the sales go to humanitarian efforts in Ukraine.
